kadhal desam ( tamil : காதல் desam ) is a 1996 tamil romantic action drama film directed by kathir and produced by k. t. kunjumon . the film features abbas , vineeth and mohini in the lead roles , while s. p. balasubrahmanyam and chandini tamilarasan in the lead roles , while s. p. balasubrahmanyam and manivannan play supporting roles . the film 's soundtrack and soundtrack was composed by a. r. rahman .